title: Trample On The River Of Immortality( Ta Sui Xian He )
alternative_titles: Trample On The River Of Immortality
summary: Ta Sui Xian He English Translated When Qin Lie realized that dignity can only be defended by strength, he took the Predestination Astrolabe and embarked on the path to become a God. He used his blood to write an immortal saga of Demons, Gods and Buddhas, a few people transcending the three realms and seeing only inches beyond! Ta Sui Xian He, Trample On The Immortals River, Trample On The River Of Immortality,  踏碎仙河, World Shattered at My Hand, Trampling Down The Immortals River To Pieces
